	(text "note 4.8A switching current != 4.8A output current\n\nabsolute theoretical max ~2.5A output current\nthis diode is only rated for 2A and i only guarantee 1A based off datahseet"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 485.648 58.928 0)
		(effects
