	(text "TODO:\n- add the rest of the gpio\n- does the other end of the antenna need GND? idk\n- pcb it\n  - double check decoupling routing\n  - make sure to place crystals and antenna filter as close as possible to MCU\n    - crystals can be far but that requires adjusting load capacitance and calculating trace capacitance is a huge pain\n  - do fancy antennas stuff ofc (impedance match everything to 50 ohms)\n  - add basic GPIO\n  - put 5V input cap as close as possible\n  - match QSPI traces"
