	(text "could use EN pin to enable/disable, but only accepts up to VIN,\nand if on USB, then VBUS is applied, and VBUS > VIN\n\nso to make it work would require running USB through it,\nwhich would be more complex and more inefficient\n\nto make it work at all would take more components than it saves"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 483.108 43.688 0)
